title: Dune: The Bene Gesserit and the Spacing Guild
itunes:title: Dune: The Bene Gesserit and the Spacing Guild
description:
In this Dune-inspired episode of Stuff to Blow Your Mind, Robert and Joe pick up where they left off in the last episode discussing the politics, philosophy and pain science of the Bene Gesserit, before diving into the spice-assisted navigation of the Spacing Guild.
